column2: Johnny Deep was the league, human being, and amazing actor ever.
column33: Warner Brothers: Justice for Johnny Depp
column34: Johnny Depp has been wrongly accused of abusing his ex wife Amber Heard who has caused him to lose roles in his career as Jack Sparrow and multiple others. Amber herself claimed that Johnny has abused her when she abused him. His last appeal was denied by the court which I feel is not fair because Amber has not lost anything but Johnny has. We as fans would like Johnny Depp be rehired and Amber be FIRED from Warner bro and Disney! #justiceforDepp
